---
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Train - Third Place Dojo</title>
<meta name="description" content="Classes and training programs at Third Place Dojo in Coudersport, PA. Kokoro-Jitsu, kids classes, teens and adults, open mat, and Gracie Garage." />
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,300&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: #F5EFE6;
    color: #1E2A38;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(20,29,39,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: #F0F4F8; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: #C94FAE; }
  .nav-logo em { font-style: normal; color: rgba(240,244,248,0.3); font-size: 0.85em; margin-left: 0.25rem; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #F0F4F8; text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { opacity: 1; color: #C94FAE; }
  .nav-cta {
    background: #C94FAE; color: #ffffff !important;
    opacity: 1 !important; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500; transition: background 0.2s !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: #a83d90 !important; }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn-primary {
    background: #C94FAE; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 3rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(201,79,174,0.35);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(201,79,174,0.5); }

  .btn-teal {
    background: #1D9E75; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 3rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(29,158,117,0.3);
  }
  .btn-teal:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(29,158,117,0.4); }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent; color: #F0F4F8; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 3rem; border: 1.5px solid rgba(240,244,248,0.25);
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; display: inline-block;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: #1D9E75; color: #1D9E75; }

  /* PAGE HEADER */
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #141d27 0%, #1E2A38 100%);
    padding: 9rem 5rem 5rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-header::after {
    content: '道場';
    position: absolute; right: 3rem; bottom: -1.5rem;
    font-family: serif; font-size: 14rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); line-height: 1; user-select: none;
  }
  .page-header-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #1D9E75; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.05; font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #C94FAE; }
  .page-header p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(240,244,248,0.6); max-width: 52ch; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  /* SECTION LABEL */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #1D9E75; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
  }

  /* SCHEDULE */
  .schedule-section {
    padding: 6rem 5rem;
    background: #F0F4F8;
    position: relative;
  }
  .schedule-section::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #C94FAE, #1D9E75);
  }
  .schedule-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #1E2A38; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .schedule-sub {
    font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8a9bb0; margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .schedule-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .schedule-day {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,42,56,0.07);
  }
  .day-name {
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #C94FAE; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .class-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,42,56,0.06);
  }
  .class-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .class-time {
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1D9E75;
    white-space: nowrap; min-width: 80px; padding-top: 0.1rem;
  }
  .class-info { flex: 1; }
  .class-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem; color: #1E2A38; font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .class-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8a9bb0; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .schedule-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem; color: #8a9bb0; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .schedule-note strong { color: #1E2A38; }

  /* PROGRAMS */
  .programs-section { padding: 6rem 5rem; background: #F5EFE6; }
  .programs-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #1E2A38; margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .programs-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;
  }
  .program-card {
    background: #F0F4F8; border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,42,56,0.07);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }
  .program-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(30,42,56,0.09); }
  .program-tag {
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: inline-block;
  }
  .program-tag.magenta { background: rgba(201,79,174,0.1); color: #C94FAE; }
  .program-tag.teal { background: rgba(29,158,117,0.1); color: #1D9E75; }
  .program-tag.slate { background: rgba(30,42,56,0.08); color: #1E2A38; }
  .program-icon { font-size: 2.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block; }
  .program-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #1E2A38; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .program-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #1E2A38; opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .program-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.2s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .program-link.magenta { color: #C94FAE; }
  .program-link.teal { color: #1D9E75; }
  .program-link.slate { color: #1E2A38; }
  .program-link:hover { gap: 0.7rem; }

  /* KJ FEATURE */
  .kj-section {
    background: #1E2A38; padding: 6rem 5rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .kj-section::before {
    content: '心術'; position: absolute; right: 2rem; bottom: -2rem;
    font-size: 14rem; font-family: serif; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    line-height: 1; user-select: none;
  }
  .kj-left { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .kj-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .kj-japanese {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic;
    color: #C94FAE; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .kj-right { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .kj-right p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(240,244,248,0.7); margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .kj-right p strong { color: #ffffff; font-weight: 600; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: #141d27; padding: 3rem 5rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .footer-brand { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #F0F4F8; opacity: 0.9; }
  .footer-brand span { color: #C94FAE; }
  .footer-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(240,244,248,0.4); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .footer-copy { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(240,244,248,0.2); margin-top: 0.35rem; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; list-style: none; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .footer-links a {
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(240,244,248,0.5); text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: #1D9E75; }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .page-header { padding: 7rem 1.75rem 3.5rem; }
    .schedule-section { padding: 4rem 1.75rem; }
    .programs-section { padding: 4rem 1.75rem; }
    .kj-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; padding: 4rem 1.75rem; }
    footer { padding: 2rem; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Third Place <span>Dojo</span> <em>道場</em></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/train" class="active">Train</a></li>
    <li><a href="/events">Events</a></li>
    <li><a href="/pricing">Pricing</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://ko-fi.com/kokorojitsu" class="nav-cta">Support Us</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<header class="page-header">
  <span class="page-header-label">Training Programs</span>
  <h1>Come learn.<br><em>Come move.</em></h1>
  <p>Classes for kids, teens, and adults. Structured curriculum, zero ego, and a community that shows up for each other. All skill levels welcome — zero experience required.</p>
</header>

<section class="schedule-section">
  <span class="section-label">Schedule</span>
  <h2 class="schedule-title">Weekly class schedule</h2>
  <p class="schedule-sub">Opening soon at 118 N. Main St., Coudersport, PA</p>

  <div class="schedule-grid">

    <div class="schedule-day">
      <span class="day-name">Monday</span>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">5:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Kids Class</div>
          <div class="class-desc">Ages 8-12 · 45 min · Kokoro-Jitsu fundamentals</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">6:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Teens and Adults</div>
          <div class="class-desc">13+ · 60 min · Kokoro-Jitsu curriculum</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="schedule-day">
      <span class="day-name">Wednesday</span>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">5:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Kids Class</div>
          <div class="class-desc">Ages 8-12 · 45 min · Kokoro-Jitsu fundamentals</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">6:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Teens and Adults</div>
          <div class="class-desc">13+ · 60 min · Kokoro-Jitsu curriculum</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="schedule-day">
      <span class="day-name">Friday</span>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">5:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Kids Class</div>
          <div class="class-desc">Ages 8-12 · 45 min · Kokoro-Jitsu fundamentals</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">6:30 PM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">Teens and Adults</div>
          <div class="class-desc">13+ · 60 min · Kokoro-Jitsu curriculum</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="schedule-day">
      <span class="day-name">Saturday</span>
      <div class="class-item">
        <span class="class-time">10:00 AM</span>
        <div class="class-info">
          <div class="class-name">The Kokoro-Jitsu Club</div>
          <div class="class-desc">Teens and adults · 2 hrs · Free / donation-based open training</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="schedule-note"><strong>Gracie Garage Open Mat</strong> — times vary. If you are studying Gracie Combatives and looking for a place to train with others, reach out through the Gracie University locator. Space and mat time are available at no cost.</p>
</section>

<section class="programs-section" id="programs">
  <span class="section-label">Programs</span>
  <h2 class="programs-title">What we offer</h2>

  <div class="programs-grid">

    <div class="program-card">
      <span class="program-icon">🧒</span>
      <span class="program-tag magenta">Kids</span>
      <h3 class="program-name">Kids Class (8-12)</h3>
      <p class="program-desc">A structured, age-appropriate introduction to Kokoro-Jitsu. Kids learn movement, coordination, basic self-defense concepts, and how to be good training partners. Confidence and respect are the real curriculum.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="program-card">
      <span class="program-icon">🥋</span>
      <span class="program-tag magenta">Teens and Adults</span>
      <h3 class="program-name">Teens and Adults</h3>
      <p class="program-desc">The full Kokoro-Jitsu curriculum. BJJ, Kenpo, Karate, and Aiki principles woven into a single living art. Structured belt ranks with objective testing. Flow-first, ego-free training culture. All experience levels welcome.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="program-card">
      <span class="program-icon">🏛️</span>
      <span class="program-tag teal">Community</span>
      <h3 class="program-name">The Kokoro-Jitsu Club</h3>
      <p class="program-desc">Saturday open training, free and donation-based. No formal curriculum — just mat time, exploration, rolling, and community. Open to teens and adults. You do not need to be a registered student to attend. Show up and train.</p>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/kokorojitsu" target="_blank" class="program-link teal">Support on Ko-fi</a>
    </div>

    <div class="program-card">
      <span class="program-icon">🤼</span>
      <span class="program-tag slate">Open Mat</span>
      <h3 class="program-name">Gracie Garage</h3>
      <p class="program-desc">Third Place Dojo is pursuing Gracie Garage affiliation through Gracie University. If you are studying Gracie Combatives and looking for training partners or mat space in Coudersport, you are welcome here. Times are arranged by contact — no drop-in fee, ever.</p>
      <a href="https://www.gracieuniversity.com/Pages/Public/Affiliates?enc=0kNCxLapRCnvSETEUrzT+Q==" target="_blank" class="program-link slate">Find Gracie Garage locations</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="kj-section">
  <div class="kj-left">
    <span class="section-label" style="color:#1D9E75;">The Martial Art</span>
    <h2 class="kj-title">Kokoro-Jitsu</h2>
    <p class="kj-japanese">こころ術</p>
    <a href="https://kokorojitsu.com" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Explore kokorojitsu.com</a>
  </div>
  <div class="kj-right">
    <p>A <strong>living martial art</strong> rooted in BJJ, Kenpo, Karate, and Aiki-Jitsu. Built around the idea that you absorb what works, discard what does not, and add what is uniquely yours.</p>
    <p>Practical, mindful, and always evolving. <strong>Objective belt testing</strong>, no politics, no performance. Just honest training and real progress.</p>
    <p>The full curriculum, rank structure, philosophy, and black belt degree system live at kokorojitsu.com.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div>
    <div class="footer-brand">Third Place <span>Dojo</span></div>
    <div class="footer-sub">118 N. Main St. · Coudersport, PA · 道場</div>
    <div class="footer-copy">Third Place Dojo 2025</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="footer-links">
    <li><a href="/train">Train</a></li>
    <li><a href="/events">Events</a></li>
    <li><a href="/pricing">Pricing</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://kokorojitsu.com" target="_blank">Kokoro-Jitsu</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://ko-fi.com/kokorojitsu" target="_blank">Ko-fi</a></li>
  </ul>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
